fields.title: Avenger
fields.review: If you like Sam Elliott's work and I do, you will very much enjoy this spy story.

fields.title: Avengers: Age of Ultron
fields.review: What also really bothered me was Ultron's voice and character. Seemed too childish and immature for a villain. His humor was also cheesy.

fields.title: Avengers: Infinity War
fields.review: Avengers infinity war is an emotional roller coaster.

fields.title: Avengers: Endgame
fields.review: I checked the row where I was sitting, and people were crying. After the movie, I was seeing people with smudged mascara.

fields.title: Star Wars: Episode I - The Phantom Menace
fields.review: Star Wars: Episode I - The Phantom Menace'. A movie, which has a difficult standing in the fan community. For me, not understandable, because I really like the movie and it's a successful prelude to the formerly new trilogy.

fields.title: Star Wars: Episode II - Attack of the Clones
Star Wars: Episode III - Revenge of the Sith
fields.review: May 19, 2005 was not a simple day for fans and fans of the Star Wars. It was a day when all pieces of history fell into place, finally opening a riddle that lasted more than 28 years. People imagined and thought out, wrote books and stories, collected facts and made legends, and everything for the sake of one saga, which will forever remain in the hearts of its admirers.
